"```sql\nSELECT comments.Text\nFROM comments\nJOIN posts ON comments.PostId = posts.Id\nWHERE posts.Title = 'How does gentle boosting differ from AdaBoost?';\n```\n\nThis SQL query selects the `Text` of all comments made on the post with the title \"How does gentle boosting differ from AdaBoost?\". It uses a JOIN operation to connect the `comments` table with the `posts` table based on the `PostId` foreign key relationship."